cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MS, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a deep learning method for automatic seed point detection in breast cancer response monitoring using MRI. This involves image classification and segmentation, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also mentions validation using pathological embedding, which falls under medical imaging (cs.MS) and multimodal learning (cs.MM).
